{"tid":1509515,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣】除咗7成外資，中國仲有咩春袋畀香港摙住？","createTime":"2019-08-27T01:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T10:38:55.000Z","uid":126510,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"059b82bce440e4457bc74828538d62a696a6dda3","tid":1509515,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:04:13.000Z","msg":"中國成日洗人腦話 香港無咗大陸唔得<br />\n但實情係最近爆得越黎越多 中國無咗香港唔得 嘅例子<br />\n<br />\n相信唔少人都feel到香港對中國都重要，但具體有幾重要，係真係見到呢d數據先咁清晰<br />\n原來7成外資係經我地香港進入大陸架？（source: 中國商務部）<br />\n原來6成內資係透過香港走向世界架？(source: HKMA 2016)<br />\n所以話，有數據+有解釋+有可靠source 大家先會對香港的重要性有個直觀的認識，講野都大聲d！我地先知道自己喺談判到有幾多籌碼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fE6RKfQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfE6RKfQ.jpg&h=8a6a52df&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XT3TXAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXT3TXAQ.jpg&h=d9a95466&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PAk3Asz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPAk3Asz.png&h=02bdc4b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QjPv0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QjPv0U.png&h=dd50ccd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/key-information/insight/20161027.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fkey-information%2Finsight%2F20161027.shtml&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=0521b344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/key-information/insight/20161027.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我懇請各位搵多d 香港對中國重要的地方<br />\n加以簡潔的解釋+可觀的數據 令大眾知道香港的重要性</span><br />\n專家就解釋+搵數據<br />\n文宣組就做靚幅圖<br />\n其他人就畀下ideas+ 推post+ spread開文宣成果<br />\n<br />\nbad example: 香港對大陸好重要，因為外資經香港進入(效果一般）<br />\ngood example: 香港對大陸好重要，因為 70%外資經香港進入（配圖配解釋）<br />\n我相信有好多其他範疇中國係要靠香港，大家可以更加詳細地羅列解釋，例如 <br />\ni)外匯儲備 （究竟大陸點通過香港換美金，換咗幾多？）<br />\nii) 進出口/轉口貿易<br />\niii)人民幣離岸服務<br />\nv) 大陸公司透過香港融資的數目<br />\niv)紅色權貴在港資產，買樓\b的內資佔咗幾多，如何洗錢<br />\nv) 其他（請補充）<br />\n<br />\n我相信連登一定好多高手可以做得好呢場戰鬥<br />\n#香港加油 #五大訴求缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b242d7fdcc69e0ebb0f95153354c29741257a7","tid":1509515,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=115b12e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=785b4748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=8f5baa8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"db2d6d2dc2d286b07f994f4c0dee9b0d4621059a","tid":1509515,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:04:58.000Z","msg":"小知識 - 原來機場控制唔只控制香港D機上落，<br />\n廣洲，深圳，澳門既飛機升降都會受香港指揮影響，搞到D飛升降唔到。。。。<br />\n大家千祈唔好搞到機場控制個班番唔到工啊 會好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/